## 1. Overview & Upgrade Steps

**Prerequisite**: Complete PF4→PF5 migration first (https://v5-archive.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade).

### Official upgrade order:
1. Update dependencies from PF5 to PF6 in `package.json`
2. Run codemods suite (`npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6`)
3. Remove all CSS overrides (PF5 CSS vars no longer work)
4. Review and update variable and class names (3 sub-codemods)
5. Update pixel-based breakpoint logic to rem-based
6. Build and test

---

## 2. Package & Dependency Changes

| Area | Change |
|------|--------|
| **Core package** | `@patternfly/react-core@5.x.x` → `@patternfly/react-core@6.x.x` |
| **Charts package** | `@patternfly/react-charts` still exists, but import paths changed |
| **Charts sub-path** | `@patternfly/react-charts` → `@patternfly/react-charts/victory` |
| **Victory dependency** | Victory is now an **optional peer dependency** — install `victory` or specific packages (`victory-core`, `victory-tooltip`, etc.) |
| **Tokens package** | `@patternfly/react-tokens` — token names changed (see Section 4) |
| **Drag & Drop** | New `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` package with `DragDropSort` component |
| **Deprecated imports** | Many components moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| **Next imports** | Components from `@patternfly/react-core/next` promoted to `@patternfly/react-core` |

---

## 3. CSS Class Name Changes

### Prefix Change
| Before | After |
|--------|-------|
| `pf-v5-c-*` | `pf-v6-c-*` |
| `pf-v5-l-*` | `pf-v6-l-*` |
| `pf-v5-u-*` | `pf-v6-u-*` |
| `pf-v5-m-*` | `pf-v6-m-*` (modifier classes) |
| `pf-v5-svg` | `pf-v6-svg` |

### Specific class changes:
- `pf-m-selectable` removed from TreeView list items
- `pf-v6-c-slider__step--Left` → `pf-v6-c-slider__step--InsetInlineStart`
- `pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--Left` → `pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--InsetInlineStart`
- `pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--Right` → `pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--InsetInlineEnd`
- `pf-v6-c-form__group-label-help` — now auto-wrapped, no need to add manually

### Tools:
- **class-name-updater codemod**: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest --v6 --fix <path>` (uses `class-name-updater` package)

---

## 4. CSS Variable / Token Changes

### Design Token System Overhaul
PF6 introduces a completely new **design token system**. The old `--pf-v5-global--*` and `--pf-v5-c-*` CSS variables are **removed**.

### Variable naming pattern change:
| PF5 Pattern | PF6 Pattern |
|-------------|-------------|
| `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` | `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg` |
| `--pf-v5-global--Color--100` | `--pf-t--global--text--color--regular` (semantic naming) |
| `--pf-v5-global--spacer--xl` | `--pf-t--global--spacer--xl` |
| `--pf-v5-global--BorderWidth--lg` | `--pf-t--global--border--width--extra-strong` |
| `--pf-v5-global--BoxShadow--sm` | `--pf-t--global--box-shadow--sm` |
| `--pf-v5-global--ZIndex--lg` | `--pf-t--global--z-index--lg` |

### React Token naming change:
| PF5 React Token | PF6 React Token |
|-----------------|-----------------|
| `global_FontSize_lg` | `t_global_font_size_lg` |
| `global_Color_100` | `t_temp_dev_tbd` (must manually replace) |
| `global_BorderWidth_lg` | `global_border_width_extra_strong` |
| `global_FontWeight_normal` | `global_font_weight_body_default` |
| `color_green_10` | `t_color_green_10` (prefixed with `t_`) |

### Key points:
- **Global non-color tokens**: auto-fixable by codemods
- **Global color tokens**: replaced with `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink) — **MUST be manually replaced**
- **Component tokens** (`--pf-v5-c-*`): must be **manually replaced** — no 1:1 mapping
- All React tokens with PF token values now prefixed with `t_`

### Reference spreadsheets:
- [Removed variables](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true)
- [Added variables](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true)

### Three token codemods:
1. **class-name-updater**: `pf-v5` → `pf-v6` prefix replacement
2. **tokens-update**: Updates CSS vars + React tokens in `.js`/`.tsx` files
3. **css-vars-updater**: Updates CSS vars in `.css`, `.scss`, `.md` files

---

## 5. Breakpoint Changes

Breakpoints changed from **pixels to rems**:

| Breakpoint | Token | PF5 (px) | PF6 (rem) |
|------------|-------|----------|-----------|
| xs | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xs` | 0px | 0rem |
| sm | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--sm` | 576px | 36rem |
| md | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--md` | 768px | 48rem |
| lg | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--lg` | 992px | 62rem |
| xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xl` | 1200px | 75rem |
| 2xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--2xl` | 1450px | 90.625rem |

**Action**: Update any hardcoded pixel-based breakpoint logic (divide by 16 for rem).

---

## 6. Component Removals & Deprecations

### Fully Removed (no deprecated path, must rewrite):
| Removed Component | Replacement |
|-------------------|-------------|
| `ApplicationLauncher` | Custom menu application launcher example |
| `ContextSelector` | Custom menu context selector example |
| `Dropdown` (old deprecated) | Composable Dropdown or Dropdown template |
| `OptionsMenu` (deprecated) | Composable Select or Select template |
| `PageHeader` (deprecated) | Masthead + Toolbar components |
| `Select` (old deprecated) | Composable Select or Select template |
| `KebabToggle` | `MenuToggle` with `variant="plain"` + `EllipsisVIcon` |
| `PageNavigation` | Removed entirely, use `PageSection` |
| `EmptyStateHeader` | No longer exported — props moved to `EmptyState` |
| `EmptyStateIcon` | No longer exported — pass `icon` prop to `EmptyState` |

### Deprecated (moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`):
| Component | Import Change | Recommended Replacement |
|-----------|---------------|------------------------|
| `Chip` | `→ deprecated` | `Label` |
| `ChipGroup` | `→ deprecated` | `LabelGroup` |
| `Tile` | `→ deprecated` | `Card` |
| `DragDrop`, `Droppable`, `Draggable` | `→ deprecated` | `DragDropSort` from `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` |
| `DualListSelector` (old) | `→ deprecated` | New DualListSelector (promoted from `/next`) |
| `Modal` (old) | `→ deprecated` | New Modal (promoted from `/next`) |

### Promoted from `/next` to main:
| Component | Old Import | New Import |
|-----------|-----------|------------|
| `DualListSelector` | `@patternfly/react-core/next` | `@patternfly/react-core` |
| `Modal` | `@patternfly/react-core/next` | `@patternfly/react-core` |

---

## 7. Component Renames

| PF5 Name | PF6 Name |
|----------|----------|
| `Text` | `Content` (with `component` prop) |
| `TextContent` | `Content` |
| `TextList` | `Content` with `component="ul"` or `component="ol"` |
| `TextListItem` | `Content` with `component="li"` |
| `TextProps` | `ContentProps` |
| `TextVariants` | `ContentVariants` |
| `TextListVariants` | `ContentVariants` |
| `TextListItemVariants` | `ContentVariants` |
| `MastheadBrand` (old) | `MastheadLogo` |
| `MastheadBrand` (new) | New wrapper component for `MastheadLogo` |
| `ToolbarChipGroupContent` | `ToolbarLabelGroupContent` |
| `ToolbarChipGroupContentProps` | `ToolbarLabelGroupContentProps` |
| `ToolbarChipGroup` | `ToolbarLabelGroup` |
| `ToolbarChip` | `ToolbarLabel` |
| `FormFiledGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` | `FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` (typo fix) |
| `InvalidObject` (component-groups) | `MissingPage` |
| `InvalidObjectProps` (component-groups) | `MissingPageProps` |
| `NotAuthorized` (component-groups) | `UnauthorizedAccess` |
| `ContentHeader` (component-groups) | `PageHeader` |
| `LogSnippetBorderVariant` (component-groups) | Use `AlertVariant` from PF core |

---

## 8. Component API / Prop Changes (Detailed)

### Accordion
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `AccordionContent` | `isHidden` prop **removed** (auto-set by `isExpanded` on AccordionItem) |
| `AccordionToggle` | `isExpanded` prop **moved to AccordionItem** |
| `AccordionItem` | Now renders a `div` wrapper (markup change) |

### Alert
- No major prop changes, but `c_alert__FontSize` CSS variable may need manual update

### Avatar
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `border` prop | **Removed** — use `isBordered` instead |

### Banner
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `variant` prop | **Removed** — use `color` or `status` props |
| `color` values | `"cyan"` → `"teal"`, `"gold"` → `"yellow"` |

### Button
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `isActive` prop | **Renamed** to `isClicked` |
| `isDisabled` | Now sets `disabled` attr, not `aria-disabled` (unless `component` ≠ "button") |
| `aria-disabled` | Only renders when `true` |
| Plain variant icons | Must use `icon` prop instead of children |
| Text wrapping | Button text now wrapped in inner `<span>` (affects `byText` queries) |
| `variant="plain"` children | Icons must be moved to `icon` prop |
| `BarsIcon` child in `PageToggleButton` | Replace with `isHamburgerButton` prop |
| `StarIcon` child | Replace with `isFavorite` / `isFavorited` props |

### Card
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `isSelectableRaised` | **Removed** |
| `isDisabledRaised` | **Removed** |
| `hasSelectableInput` | **Removed** |
| `selectableInputAriaLabel` | **Removed** |
| `onSelectableInputChange` | **Removed** |
| `isFlat` | **Removed** |
| `isRounded` | **Removed** |
| Clickable cards | `selectableActions.selectableActionId` and `selectableActions.name` no longer needed |

### Checkbox / Radio
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `isLabelBeforeButton` | **Replaced** with `labelPosition="start"` |

### Chip → Label
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `Chip` component | Deprecated → use `Label` |
| `ChipGroup` | Deprecated → use `LabelGroup` |
| `Chip.onClick` | → `Label.onClose` |
| `Chip.badge` | Move badge as child of Label |
| `Chip.numChips` | → `Label.numLabels` |
| `Label` variant | Add `variant="outline"` to match Chip appearance |

### Data List
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `DataListAction.isPlainButtonAction` | **Removed** |

### Drawer
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `DrawerHead.hasNoPadding` | **Removed** |
| `DrawerContent.colorVariant="no-background"` | **Removed** (new `"primary"` value added) |
| `DrawerContent/PanelContent/Section.colorVariant="light-200"` | → `"secondary"` |
| `DrawerColorVariant.light200` | → `DrawerColorVariant.secondary` |
| `DrawerHead` | No longer renders `DrawerPanelBody` internally |

### DualListSelector
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| Old implementation | Deprecated → `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| New implementation | Promoted from `@patternfly/react-core/next` |

### EmptyState ⚠️ (Major refactor — partially manual)
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `EmptyStateHeader` | **No longer exported** — use props on `EmptyState` directly |
| `EmptyStateIcon` | **No longer exported** — pass `icon` prop to `EmptyState` |
| `EmptyStateHeader.titleText` | → `EmptyState.titleText` |
| `EmptyStateHeader.headingLevel` | → `EmptyState.headingLevel` |
| `EmptyStateHeader.icon` | → `EmptyState.icon={CubesIcon}` (component ref, not JSX) |
| `EmptyStateHeader.className` | → `EmptyState.headerClassName` |

### ExpandableSection
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `isActive` prop | **Removed** |

### FormGroup
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `labelIcon` prop | **Renamed** to `labelHelp` |
| Label help markup | Now auto-wrapped in `<span className="pf-v6-c-form__group-label-help">` |

### HelperTextItem
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `hasIcon` prop | **Removed** (auto-renders when variant ≠ "default") |
| `isDynamic` prop | **Removed** |
| `screenReaderText` | Now renders only when variant ≠ "default" |

### JumpLinksItem
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `href` prop | Now **required** |
| Internal markup | Uses Button component internally |
| `onClick` type | `React.MouseEvent` (was `React.MouseEvent<HTMLAnchorElement>`) |

### Label
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `isOverflowLabel` | **Replaced** with `variant="overflow"` |
| `color="cyan"` | → `color="teal"` |
| `color="gold"` | → `color="yellow"` |

### LoginMainFooterLinksItem
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| Props removed | `href`, `linkComponentProps` etc. — now pass children directly with Button |
| LoginMainHeader | Renders `div` instead of `header` element |

### Masthead ⚠️ (Structure change)
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `MastheadBrand` (old) | **Renamed** to `MastheadLogo` |
| `MastheadBrand` (new) | New wrapper component |
| `backgroundColor` prop | **Removed** |
| Structure | `MastheadToggle` + `MastheadBrand` must be inside `MastheadMain` |

### MenuToggle
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `splitButtonOptions` prop | **Replaced** with `splitButtonItems` |
| `SplitButtonOptions` interface | **Deleted** |
| Icon-only toggles | Pass icon to `icon` prop, not as children |

### Modal
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| Old implementation | Deprecated → `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| New implementation | Promoted from `@patternfly/react-core/next` |

### Nav
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `variant="tertiary"` | → `variant="horizontal-subnav"` |
| `theme` prop | **Removed** |

### NavItem
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `hasNavLinkWrapper` prop | **Removed** |
| Icons | Pass to new `icon` prop |

### Page
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `header` prop | **Renamed** to `masthead` |
| `tertiaryNav` prop | **Renamed** to `horizontalSubnav` |
| `isTertiaryNavGrouped` | **Renamed** to `isHorizontalSubnavGrouped` |
| `isTertiaryNavWidthLimited` | **Renamed** to `isHorizontalSubnavWidthLimited` |
| Markup | When `horizontalSubnav` or `breadcrumb` passed, contents wrapped in `PageBody` |

### PageBreadcrumb / PageSection
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `isWidthLimited` | No longer controls `PageBody` wrapping — use new `hasBodyWrapper` prop |
| `PageSection.variant` | Only accepts `"default"` or `"secondary"` (dark, light etc. removed) |
| `PageSection.type="nav"` | **Removed** |
| `PageNavigation` component | **Removed** entirely |
| `PageSidebar.theme` prop | **Removed** |
| `PageHeaderToolsItem.isSelected` | **Removed** |

### Popper / Dropdown / Select
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `appendTo` default | Changed to `document.body` |

### SimpleFileUpload
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `aria-describedby` | Removed from internal TextInput |
| Browse button `id` | Removed — use `browseButtonAriaDescribedby` prop |
| Helper text | Use `FileUploadHelperText` as child instead of `FormHelperText` |

### Switch
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `labelOff` prop | **Removed** |

### Tabs
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `isSecondary` prop | **Renamed** to `isSubtab` |
| `variant="light300"` | → `variant="secondary"` |
| Scroll buttons | Now use Button components internally with wrapper div |

### WizardStep
| Change | Detail |
|--------|--------|
| `body` prop | No longer accepts `null` |
| WizardFooter | Now uses ActionList internally |
| WizardNavItem | New wrapper `.pf-v6-c-wizard__nav-link-main` around content |

---

## 9. Chart Changes

### Import Path Change (BREAKING)
```
// PF5
import { Chart, ChartArea, ChartBar } from '@patternfly/react-charts';

// PF6
import { Chart, ChartArea, ChartBar } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory';
```

### Victory Dependency
- Victory is now an **optional peer dependency**
- Install `victory` (all features) OR specific packages:
  - `victory-core`
  - `victory-tooltip`
  - `victory-chart`
  - etc.

### LogViewer Styles
- Stylesheet moved from PatternFly package into `@patternfly/react-log-viewer` itself
- May need to import `@patternfly/react-log-viewer/dist/esm/...` stylesheet manually

---

## 10. Icon Changes

- `BarsIcon` in `PageToggleButton`: Replace with `isHamburgerButton` prop
- `StarIcon` in `Button`: Replace with `isFavorite`/`isFavorited` props
- Icons in plain buttons: Must use `icon` prop (not children)
- Icons in NavItem: Must use new `icon` prop
- Icons in MenuToggle: Must use `icon` prop (not children)
- `KebabToggle`: Replaced with `MenuToggle variant="plain" icon={<EllipsisVIcon />}`

---

## 11. Layout Changes

- Layout class prefix: `pf-v5-l-*` → `pf-v6-l-*`
- Logical direction CSS properties used (InsetInlineStart/End instead of Left/Right)
- Breakpoints: pixels → rems (see Section 5)

---

## 12. Toolbar Changes

### Prop Renames (Chip → Label terminology)
| Component | Old Prop | New Prop |
|-----------|----------|----------|
| `Toolbar` | `customChipGroupContent` | `customLabelGroupContent` |
| `ToolbarExpandableContent` | `chipContainerRef` | `labelContainerRef` |
| `ToolbarFilter` | `chips` | `labels` |
| `ToolbarFilter` | `deleteChipGroup` | `deleteLabelGroup` |
| `ToolbarFilter` | `deleteChip` | `deleteLabel` |
| `ToolbarFilter` | `chipGroupExpandedText` | `labelGroupExpandedText` |
| `ToolbarFilter` | `chipGroupCollapsedText` | `labelGroupCollapsedText` |
| `ToolbarFilter` | `expandableChipContainerRef` | `expandableLabelContainerRef` |
| `ToolbarChipGroupContent` | `chipGroupContentRef` | `labelGroupContentRef` |
| `ToolbarChipGroupContent` | `customChipGroupContent` | `customLabelGroupContent` |
| `ToolbarToggleGroup` | `chipContainerRef` | `labelContainerRef` |

### Variant Renames
| Component | Old Variant | New Variant |
|-----------|-------------|-------------|
| `ToolbarGroup` / `ToolbarToggleGroup` | `button-group` | `action-group` |
| `ToolbarGroup` / `ToolbarToggleGroup` | `icon-button-group` | `action-group-plain` |

### ToolbarItem variant removals
- `"bulk-select"` — **removed**
- `"overflow-menu"` — **removed**
- `"search-filter"` — **removed**
- `"chip-group"` → `"label-group"`

### Removed Props
| Component | Removed Prop | Replacement |
|-----------|-------------|-------------|
| `Toolbar` | `usePageInsets` | — |
| `ToolbarContent` | `alignSelf` | — |
| `ToolbarItem` | `widths` | — |
| `ToolbarToggleGroup` | `alignment` | — |
| `ToolbarGroup/Item/ToggleGroup` | `spacer` | Use `gap`, `columnGap`, `rowGap` |
| `ToolbarGroup/ToggleGroup` | `spaceItems` | Use `gap`, `columnGap`, `rowGap` |

### Alignment Value Changes
| Old Value | New Value |
|-----------|-----------|
| `alignLeft` | `alignStart` |
| `alignRight` | `alignEnd` |

---

## 13. Test Breakage Patterns

### Button Tests
1. **`aria-disabled` not found**: Button's `isDisabled` now sets `disabled` attr, not `aria-disabled`. Remove tests checking `aria-disabled="false"`.
2. **`byText` queries fail**: Button text wrapped in inner `<span>`. Use `byRole('button', { name: '...' })` instead.

### Select Tests
1. **`Cannot find role`**: Popper menu may be `aria-disabled` after selection. Pass `{hidden: true}` option or set `appendTo="inline"`.

### Snapshot Tests
- All `pf-v5-*` classes → `pf-v6-*`
- `pf-m-selectable` removed from TreeView
- Various markup structure changes (Accordion, Button, Masthead, Wizard, Pagination, Tabs)
- OUIA component types: `PF5/` → `PF6/`

---

## 14. Codemod Tools

### Main codemods
```bash
# Step 1: Dry run (see issues)
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6

# Step 2: Auto-fix
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --fix

# Step 3: Cleanup data-codemods attributes (run ONCE after all other codemods)
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --only data-codemods-cleanup --fix
```

### CSS class name updater
```bash
npx @patternfly/class-name-updater <path-to-src> --v6 --fix
```

### CSS vars updater (for .css, .scss, .md files)
```bash
npx @patternfly/css-vars-updater <path-to-src>
```

### Enable animations (optional)
```bash
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --only enable-animations --fix
```

### Components supporting `hasAnimations`:
- `AlertGroup`
- `DualListSelector` (when `isTree` is truthy)
- `FormFieldGroupExpandable`
- `SearchInputExpandable`
- `TreeView`
- `Table` (from `@patternfly/react-table`)

---

## 15. Quick Evaluation Checklist

Use this to evaluate whether a migration branch is complete:

### ✅ Package & Imports
- [ ] All `@patternfly/*` packages updated to v6
- [ ] No imports from `@patternfly/react-core/next` (should be promoted)
- [ ] Deprecated components imported from `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`
- [ ] Chart imports use `@patternfly/react-charts/victory` sub-path
- [ ] Victory peer dependency installed
- [ ] No `data-codemods` attributes remaining in code

### ✅ CSS Classes
- [ ] No `pf-v5-` prefixed class names remain
- [ ] All classes use `pf-v6-` prefix
- [ ] Logical direction properties used (InsetInlineStart/End vs Left/Right)

### ✅ CSS Variables / Tokens
- [ ] No `--pf-v5-*` CSS variables remain
- [ ] No `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` temporary tokens remain (all replaced)
- [ ] React tokens use new `t_` prefix where applicable
- [ ] Component-specific tokens manually updated
- [ ] CSS overrides reviewed and updated or removed

### ✅ Component API
- [ ] `Chip`/`ChipGroup` → `Label`/`LabelGroup` or deprecated import
- [ ] `Tile` → `Card` or deprecated import
- [ ] `Text`/`TextContent`/`TextList`/`TextListItem` → `Content`
- [ ] `EmptyState` refactored (no EmptyStateHeader/EmptyStateIcon as children)
- [ ] `MastheadBrand` → `MastheadLogo` (wrapped in new `MastheadBrand`)
- [ ] `Page.header` → `Page.masthead`
- [ ] All tertiary nav props renamed to horizontal-subnav equivalents
- [ ] `Button.isActive` → `Button.isClicked`
- [ ] Icons in Button use `icon` prop (not children)
- [ ] `Tabs.isSecondary` → `Tabs.isSubtab`
- [ ] Toolbar chip-related props renamed to label equivalents
- [ ] Toolbar spacer/spaceItems → gap/columnGap/rowGap
- [ ] `FormGroup.labelIcon` → `FormGroup.labelHelp`
- [ ] `MenuToggle.splitButtonOptions` → `splitButtonItems`
- [ ] Drawer colorVariant values updated
- [ ] Card selection-related props removed
- [ ] All removed deprecated components replaced

### ✅ Breakpoints
- [ ] No hardcoded pixel breakpoints matching old PF values
- [ ] Breakpoint logic uses rem values or PF6 tokens

### ✅ Tests
- [ ] Snapshot tests updated for PF6 markup
- [ ] Button tests don't rely on `aria-disabled` attribute
- [ ] Button tests use `byRole` instead of `byText` where needed
- [ ] Select tests handle Popper `appendTo` default change
- [ ] TreeView tests don't rely on `pf-m-selectable` class

### ✅ Theming
- [ ] No `theme="dark"` / `theme="light"` props on Nav, PageSidebar
- [ ] No `backgroundColor` prop on Masthead
- [ ] No `border="dark"` on Avatar (use `isBordered`)
- [ ] CSS overrides removed or mapped to new design tokens


