<!-- Modal Migration -->
<details>
  <summary>🪟 Modal Component Migration <span class="winner-tag">semver/goose wins</span></summary>
  <div class="details-content">
    <h4>What changed in PF6</h4>
    <p>The old Modal is deprecated and moved to <code>@patternfly/react-core/deprecated</code>. The new PF6 Modal (promoted from <code>/next</code>) uses a composable API with <code>ModalHeader</code>, <code>ModalBody</code>, and <code>ModalFooter</code> children instead of props like <code>title</code>, <code>showClose</code>, and <code>hasNoBodyWrapper</code>.</p>

    <h4>pf-codemods approach</h4>
    <pre><code><span class="diff-del">- import { Modal, ModalVariant } from '@patternfly/react-core';</span>
<span class="diff-add">+ import { Modal, ModalVariant } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';</span>

// No other changes — same props, same usage pattern</code></pre>
    <p>Moves Modal to the deprecated import path. This is the minimum codemod output — it delays migration rather than completing it. Since PF5 packages are still installed, the <code>/deprecated</code> subpath doesn't even exist, causing 18 build errors.</p>

    <h4>semver/goose approach</h4>
    <pre><code><span class="diff-add">+ import { Modal, ModalHeader, ModalVariant } from '@patternfly/react-core';</span>

// Before:
<span class="diff-del">- &lt;Modal title={t('Edit site')} variant={ModalVariant.medium}
-   isOpen={isModalOpen} showClose={false}&gt;</span>

// After:
<span class="diff-add">+ &lt;Modal variant={ModalVariant.medium} isOpen={isModalOpen}&gt;
+   &lt;ModalHeader title={t('Edit site')} /&gt;</span></code></pre>
    <p>Uses the new PF6 composable Modal API. Removes deprecated props (<code>title</code>, <code>showClose</code>, <code>hasNoBodyWrapper</code>) and adds <code>ModalHeader</code> as a child component. Applied across all 10 Modal usages.</p>

    <h4>Build impact</h4>
    <p>However, <strong>both branches still have build errors</strong> for Modal. semver/goose's errors are for leftover <code>showClose</code> and <code>hasNoBodyWrapper</code> props that weren't fully removed in some files (11 type errors). pf-codemods has 18 import errors because <code>/deprecated</code> doesn't exist in PF5.</p>

    <table class="cmp-table">
      <tr><td>Strategy</td><td>pf-codemods: deprecated compat</td><td>semver/goose: new PF6 API</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Build errors</td><td>18 (import failures)</td><td>11 (prop cleanup needed)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Future-proof?</td><td>❌ Deprecated code</td><td>✅ Forward-looking</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</details>

<!-- EmptyState -->
