    <h4>pf-codemods approach</h4>
    <pre><code>// EmptyData/index.tsx — awkward titleText wrapping:
<span class="diff-add">+ &lt;EmptyState titleText={&lt;Title headingLevel="h2" size="lg"&gt;
+     {message || t('Data not found')}
+   &lt;/Title&gt;} variant={EmptyStateVariant.lg}&gt;
+   {icon && &lt;EmptyStateIcon icon={icon} /&gt;}</span>

// Loading/index.tsx — whitespace artifacts:
<span class="diff-add">+ &lt;EmptyState   icon={Spinner}  &gt;</span></code></pre>
    <p>Partially applies the restructuring. <code>EmptyStateHeader</code> is removed but <code>EmptyStateIcon</code> remains as a child in EmptyData. Wraps a full <code>&lt;Title&gt;</code> JSX element inside <code>titleText</code> (non-idiomatic). Double-space formatting artifacts from automated tool.</p>

    <h4>semver/goose approach</h4>
    <pre><code>// EmptyData/index.tsx — clean prop migration:
<span class="diff-add">+ &lt;EmptyState variant={EmptyStateVariant.lg} isFullHeight
+   data-testid="sk-emptydata" icon={icon}&gt;
+   &lt;Title headingLevel="h2" size="lg"&gt;</span>

// Loading/index.tsx — clean:
<span class="diff-add">+ &lt;EmptyState icon={Spinner}&gt;</span></code></pre>
    <p>Clean prop-based migration. <code>icon</code> moved to prop on EmptyState. No formatting artifacts. <code>&lt;Title&gt;</code> left as a child element (readable).</p>

    <h4>Build impact</h4>
